---
import { Heart } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<div class="announcement-widget">
  <button class="announcement-button glass-panel" type="button" data-announcement-open aria-haspopup="dialog">
    <Heart size={18} fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" />
    <span>今日公告</span>
  </button>
  <dialog class="announcement-dialog glass-panel" data-announcement-dialog aria-label="今日公告">
    <form method="dialog">
      <button class="icon-button" value="close" aria-label="关闭公告">×</button>
    </form>
    <p class="eyebrow">TODAY</p>
    <h2>公告</h2>
    <p>
      📢 期末复习已经结束啦，博客恢复正常更新中。接下来会继续整理项目记录、折腾笔记和一些学习复盘，
      之前欠下的内容也会慢慢补回来 (｀・ω・´)
    </p>
    <a class="announcement-link" href="/me/">了解更多</a>
  </dialog>
</div>
